Description:
    Creates a new basic derby 0.6 application.

Options:
    Jade: Include Jade

Example:
    yo derby [--coffee]

    This will create:
        Gruntfile.js: Configuration for the task runner.
        _bower.json: Front-end packages installed by bower.
        _package.json: Development packages installed by npm.

        src/: Your application files.
        test/: Unit tests for your application.